


<div class="content-overlay">
  <header>
    <h1>Gaming App 2025</h1>
    <p> A showcase of the best moments with my friends through a wide variety of games!</p>
  </header> 

  <h2>Why a Gaming App</h2> 
  <p>The application's goal is to fulfill passion but also display the skills I've garnered over the past year.</p>
  <p>It has allowed me to have fun with what I do while weaving in another great passion of mine.</p>

  <h3>How do I make my way around?</h3>
  <p>There's an about page, a recordings page with clips, and search functionality by title or game.</p>

  <h4>I hope you enjoy your visit!</h4>
</div>

<div class="stats-grid">
  <div class="stat-card">
    <span class="stat-icon">🎮</span>
    <h5>Total Recordings</h5>
    <p><%= @total_recordings %></p>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-card">
    <span class="stat-icon">🎞️</span>
    <h5>Total Clips</h5>
    <p><%= @total_clips %></p>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-card">
    <span class="stat-icon">⏱️</span>
    <h5>Total Hours</h5>
    <p><%= number_with_precision(@total_hours, precision: 2) %> hrs</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="recent-section">
  <h2>🎯 Recent Gaming Sessions</h2>
  <div class="recent-grid">
    <% @recent_recordings.each do |recording| %>
      <%= link_to recording_path(recording), class: "recent-card" do %>
        <h3><%= recording.title %></h3>
        <p class="game-name"><%= recording.game_name %></p>
        <p class="date-played"><%= recording.date_played.strftime("%b %d") %></p>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="cta-section">
  <%= link_to "📹 Upload New Recording", new_recording_path, class: "cta-button" %>
</div>

